Falxugons are "harvester devils," lesser Baatezu dedicated to tempting mortal souls toward law and evil through Faustian bargains.  They resemble handsome tieflings in their true form, but can change shape to pass as mortals. 
The Minister of Mortal Relations in the Dark Eight is Furcas.
Source: Fiendish Codex II: Tyrants of the Nine Hells
